    "FromGenerative Tasks to Method Design.",
    "Based on the previously summarized generative tasks, we first categorize representative diffusion-based methods applied to solve each problem.",
    "We specifically focus on controllable generation, content editing, and stylization which together take up more than 80% of research focuses in generative/method-based research.Controllable generation.",
